win11-window-tiling-gnome — Debian GNOME Edition
================================================

Windows 11-style window tiling for Debian with GNOME and Tiling Shell.

Install
-------

  sudo dpkg -i win11-window-tiling-gnome_1.0.0_all.deb
  sudo apt install -f

Setup
-----

  win11-tiling-setup

Log out and back in after setup.

License: Tiling Shell GPL-3.0-or-later; scripts MIT.